    {
      "id": "e-preproc-text", "type": "text",
      "x": 427, "y": 378, "width": 546, "height": 220, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null, "seed": 113, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 113,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "02_image_processing.ipynb\n\n1. Assign NoData -> S2   (invalid px replaced with -9999)\n2. Assign NoData -> CDL  (declare nodata = 0 before any resampling)\n3. Filter CDL classes    (keep target crop classes, rest -> background)\n4. Resample CDL 30m -> 10m  (nearest neighbor, categorical-safe)\n5. Clip both to intersection extent  (align S2 and CDL)\n6. Extract band subset   (optional, from clipped S2)",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "02_image_processing.ipynb\n\n1. Assign NoData -> S2   (invalid px replaced with -9999)\n2. Assign NoData -> CDL  (declare nodata = 0 before any resampling)\n3. Filter CDL classes    (keep target crop classes, rest -> background)\n4. Resample CDL 30m -> 10m  (nearest neighbor, categorical-safe)\n5. Clip both to intersection extent  (align S2 and CDL)\n6. Extract band subset   (optional, from clipped S2)",
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
