    {
      "id": "e-s1-rect", "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 82, "y": 832, "width": 382, "height": 385, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c", "backgroundColor": "#fff4e6",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 120, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 120,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "e-s1-text", "type": "text",
      "x": 94, "y": 842, "width": 358, "height": 365, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null, "seed": 121, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 121,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "STAGE 1 -- Filter Preselection\n(cheap | pixel statistics only)\n________________________________\n\n[1] Global Separation Index (GSI)\n    SI = |us - uo| / 1.96*(ss + so)\n    mean over all class pairs\n\n[2] RF Feature Importance\n    Gini impurity decrease\n    RandomForest (200 trees)\n\n[3] Joint Score\n    Score = a*GSI_norm + (1-a)*RF_norm\n    a = 0.5  (equal weighting)\n\n--> Output: Top-25 candidates",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STAGE 1 -- Filter Preselection\n(cheap | pixel statistics only)\n________________________________\n\n[1] Global Separation Index (GSI)\n    SI = |us - uo| / 1.96*(ss + so)\n    mean over all class pairs\n\n[2] RF Feature Importance\n    Gini impurity decrease\n    RandomForest (200 trees)\n\n[3] Joint Score\n    Score = a*GSI_norm + (1-a)*RF_norm\n    a = 0.5  (equal weighting)\n\n--> Output: Top-25 candidates",
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "e-stage2-rect", "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 509, "y": 832, "width": 382, "height": 385, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#c2255c", "backgroundColor": "#ffe0f0",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 122, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 122,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "e-stage2-text", "type": "text",
      "x": 521, "y": 842, "width": 358, "height": 365, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null, "seed": 123, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 123,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "STAGE 2 -- CNN Forward Selection\n(novel | segmentation oracle)\n________________________________\n\nModel: lightweight U-Net (ResNet18)\nPatch: 128x128  |  Epochs: 15 max\nEarly stop: patience = 5\n\nGreedy loop (per candidate band):\n  - train on current band subset\n  - evaluate validation mIoU\n  - mIoU_new > mIoU_prev + d (0.005)?\n      YES -> accept band\n      NO  -> reject, no_improve++\n\nStop: 3 rejections OR max 15 bands\n\n--> Output: ~10-15 optimal channels",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STAGE 2 -- CNN Forward Selection\n(novel | segmentation oracle)\n________________________________\n\nModel: lightweight U-Net (ResNet18)\nPatch: 128x128  |  Epochs: 15 max\nEarly stop: patience = 5\n\nGreedy loop (per candidate band):\n  - train on current band subset\n  - evaluate validation mIoU\n  - mIoU_new > mIoU_prev + d (0.005)?\n      YES -> accept band\n      NO  -> reject, no_improve++\n\nStop: 3 rejections OR max 15 bands\n\n--> Output: ~10-15 optimal channels",
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "e-s3-rect", "type": "rectangle",
