      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Training  (05-09_segmentation_model_*.ipynb)\n\nChip Strategy:\n  Feature analysis phase  ->  on-the-fly stacking in DataLoader  (no re-chipping when band config changes)\n  After final config fixed  ->  pre-stack ~12ch chips (~32 GB, faster I/O for final training)\n\n  Year 2022  (25 files | ~10,000 chips)  ->  Train from scratch  ->  best checkpoint\n                                                     | Transfer Learning\n  Year 2023  (25 files | ~10,000 chips)  ->  Fine-tune last layers  ->  final model\n\n  Models: U-Net  |  DeepLabV3+  |  SegFormer         GPU: RTX 4090 (24 GB)  |  Batch = 8  |  Patch 256x256",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Training  (05-09_segmentation_model_*.ipynb)\n\nChip Strategy:\n  Feature analysis phase  ->  on-the-fly stacking in DataLoader  (no re-chipping when band config changes)\n  After final config fixed  ->  pre-stack ~12ch chips (~32 GB, faster I/O for final training)\n\n  Year 2022  (25 files | ~10,000 chips)  ->  Train from scratch  ->  best checkpoint\n                                                     | Transfer Learning\n  Year 2023  (25 files | ~10,000 chips)  ->  Fine-tune last layers  ->  final model\n\n  Models: U-Net  |  DeepLabV3+  |  SegFormer         GPU: RTX 4090 (24 GB)  |  Batch = 8  |  Patch 256x256",
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
